{"tid":2132821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國火星探測器「毅力號」成功發射","createTime":"2020-07-30T15:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T16:30:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7475a3de4fee98e9b95f4f61475e3967427017cf","tid":2132821,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540907-20200730.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540907-20200730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSoleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c35f1690\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540907-20200730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=30b8231d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540907-20200730.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署的火星探測器「毅力號」成功發射，並已進入預定軌道，預計明年2月抵達火星。<br />\n<br />\n「毅力號」在美國東岸時間星期四早上近8時，在佛羅里達州卡納維拉爾角基地，由「擎天神5號」火箭搭載升空，執行耗資24億美元的探索任務。<br />\n<br />\n「毅力號」配備特殊設計的傳感器，以及自主飛行的小型無人機，主要任務是分析火星的地理與環境特徵，以及採集岩石與沉積物樣本，期望在火星表面，發現古老微生物的證據。"},{"pid":"256c51eb13d356e6f5b3e87020f03cf6ee213050","tid":2132821,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"掟左落地先放無人機？"},{"pid":"c86a60afe11ff37ed573ac3c8f837659f1733891","tid":2132821,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"24億美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e82b4493ec0039e102bccc7b86388d3d1794d2e","tid":2132821,"uid":201751,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"1萬億人工島唔知為乜 VS 24億美元去火星科研<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd8933f13ec3cf552d309bfddb95fe0f904f6a3","tid":2132821,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"256c51eb13d356e6f5b3e87020f03cf6ee213050","tid":2132821,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"掟左落地先放無人機？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"應該係，之後太陽能充電<br />\n算唔算係首次民間科技領先太空科技？"},{"pid":"7dd2d74193547cf9d77eaf3f76131ab96ff1fa80","tid":2132821,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"個劇本咁似火星小強<br />\n鬥快去到火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458318a63b31559734f4b1767e7ddce727c0c7c6","tid":2132821,"uid":253608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd2d74193547cf9d77eaf3f76131ab96ff1fa80","tid":2132821,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"個劇本咁似火星小強<br />\n鬥快去到火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"鬥咩快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔計USSR<br />\n<br />\n1971年5月30日，水手9號發射升空，這是有史以來第一枚成功進入環繞火星軌道的探測器，取得了空前的成功。水手9號於1971年11月14日到達火星，在火星軌道上工作了將近一年之久，發回了7329張照片，覆蓋了火星表面超過80%的部分，同時還對火星的兩顆衛星進行了探測。<br />\n<br />\n維京1號於1975年8月20日發射升空，軌道器於1976年6月19日進入環繞火星軌道，着陸器於1976年7月20日在火星表面成功着陸。海盜2號於1975年9月9日發射升空，軌道器於1976年8月7日進入環繞火星軌道，着陸器於1976年9月3日在火星表面成功着陸。維京1號成為第一枚在火星上着陸，並且成功向地球發回照片的探測器。"},{"pid":"b502e6096dc9e283eb76d24831e311b94cd42671","tid":2132821,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd2d74193547cf9d77eaf3f76131ab96ff1fa80","tid":2132821,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"個劇本咁似火星小強<br />\n鬥快去到火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"蘇聯好早去過<br />\n<br />\n美國已去過N次<br />\n<br />\n你係咪被中國洗腦洗到SHORT咗, 以為今日係人類首次出發火星?"},{"pid":"dfe5ad9a6a6c18458f610151ab3489c2ce4369ca","tid":2132821,"uid":296705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b502e6096dc9e283eb76d24831e311b94cd42671","tid":2132821,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd2d74193547cf9d77eaf3f76131ab96ff1fa80","tid":2132821,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"個劇本咁似火星小強<br />\n鬥快去到火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"蘇聯好早去過<br />\n<br />\n美國已去過N次<br />\n<br />\n你係咪被中國洗腦洗到SHORT咗, 以為今日係人類首次出發火星?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"USA <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}